# Phil – Knowledge Navigator  /  Environment Configuration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to backend/.env and fill in your credentials.
# NEVER commit backend/.env — it is listed in .gitignore.
# If you accidentally expose a key, rotate it immediately.

# ── LLM: Cloud (Anthropic Claude) ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Required for cloud LLM mode.  Get your key at https://console.anthropic.com
# Format: sk-ant-api03-...
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-DEIN-KEY-HIER

# ── LLM: OpenAI ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Required for:
#   • Text-to-Speech (TTS) — Phil reads messages aloud
#   • ChromaDB embeddings (knowledge store + memory store)
# Get your key at https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# Format: sk-proj-...
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-DEIN-OPENAI-KEY-HIER

# ── Google Calendar / Gmail (gog CLI) ────────────────────────────────────────
# Phil uses the `gog` CLI binary to read and write Google Calendar events.
# Install gog and authenticate once:  gog auth login
# Then set GOG_ACCOUNT to your Gmail address.
GOG_ACCOUNT=deine@gmail.com

# Required in Docker (keyring is unavailable in containers).
# On the host: gog auth login  →  exports the OAuth token password.
# Leave empty for local dev (keyring is used automatically).
GOG_KEYRING_PASSWORD=

# ── LLM: Local (LM Studio / Ollama) ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Optional. If set, Phil tries the local LLM first and falls back to
# Anthropic if the local server is unreachable.
# LM Studio default: http://localhost:1234/v1
# Ollama default:    http://localhost:11434/v1
LOCAL_LLM_ENDPOINT=http://localhost:1234/v1
LOCAL_LLM_MODEL=qwen2.5-32b-instruct

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Exchange / IMAP credentials are NOT configured here.
# They are entered via the app's login screen at runtime and are held in
# memory only — they are never written to disk or sent outside your machine.
# Supported institutions:  THWS (IMAP + EWS)  |  Microsoft 365 (EWS)  |  Generic IMAP
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
